&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2025-07-01&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/047117a4-5d78-4076-a6ee-b5be74d7236e" alt="image" /&gt;
&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c7a5a91f-39aa-4305-a898-eaa3d39ea9e7" alt="image" /&gt;
&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/84884c6c-5a69-4f9f-93ca-0f3c945bb0ae" alt="image" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;새로산기여운케이스랑 마고플레인이랑 저속노화좌 없었으면 멘탈 부셔졌을거같은데 다행히 마무리까지끝냈다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;준비하는동안 24기광수책이랑 정희원의저속노화 너무 읽고싶었는데 이제읽을수있으니까 좋다.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>ADsP 45회</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/career1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 05 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/career1/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="adsp-45회"&gt;
